description: This dataset describes the value of various sectors of the Economy such as Agriculture and Foresty, Fishing, Mining, and Quarrying, manufacturing, Electricity Supply water supply, transport and communication, education, health care services etc in order to quantify  the national gross domestic product for the years 2001 - 2009
